\f0\b ## 1. Project Overview\

\f1\b0 \
\
This project is the backend of a role-based system that combines CLASSIC BANKING workflows and CRYPTO ASSET MANAGEMENT.\
\
The system models a controlled environment where financial operations are not executed directly, but instead go through a structured process involving\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}explicit business rules\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}clearly defined roles\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}strict access control rules for users\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}approval-based transaction processes\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
The primary goal of the project is not to build a production-ready exchange, but to DESIGN and IMPLEMENT a consistent domain model that reflects how such a system could behave under REAL-WORLD CONSTRAINTS.\
\
Key capabilities of the system\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Organizational hierarchy management (Center->Branch->Employee)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Customer and wallet management\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Multi-asset wallet structure (crypto-based)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Transaction request and approval workflow\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Deposit and withdrawal operations \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Asset conversion with fee handling\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Immutable transaction recording\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Role-based data scoping and authorization\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
The project is implemented as a modular monolith. Focused on clarity of design rather than distribution complexity.\
\
