\f0\b \cf0 ## 2. Domain Model\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 \
\
The system is divided into two main domains:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Organization Domain\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Banking Domain\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	a)	Organization Domain\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
This domain defines the structure of the system and determines how user access is scoped.\
\
Center->Branch->Employee\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}A Center is a high-level organizational unit.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}A Branch operates under a specific center.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}An Employee belongs either to a center or a branch depending on their role.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
This hierarchy is critical because all ACCESS CONTROL DECISIONS are derived from it.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	b)	Banking Domain\
\
This domain handles financial entities and operations.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Customer->Wallet->WalletAsset (Coin + Amount)\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}A Customer is a global entity. It is not directly tied to a branch.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}A Wallet belongs to a specific branch.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}A WalletAsset represents a specific coin balance within a wallet.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
Wallets store MULTIPLE ASSETS instead of having a single balance.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}multi-currency support\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}precise validation\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}realistic crypto behavior\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Transaction Model\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
The system does NOT allow direct transfers between wallets.\
Instead, it enforces a TWO-STEP PROCESS\
TransactionRequest->(Approval)->Transaction\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}A TransactionRequest represents an INTENTION to transfer assets.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}A Transaction is created ONLY AFTER approval.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Transactions are IMMUTABLE once created.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
