\f0\b ## 3. Roles and Responsibilities\

\f1\b0 \
\
The system is strictly ROLE-DRIVEN. Each role has clearly defined RESPONSIBILITIES and access BOUNDARIES.\
Below are the roles and information about them within the domain:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	a)	}ORG_ADMIN\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
Has GLOBAL AUTHORITY within the system. Is responsible for system setup. Can CREATE and MANAGE centers, branches, employees. Has unrestricted access to all data.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	b) 	BRANCH_OPERATOR\
\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 This role is the MAIN ENTRY POINT for financial ACTIVITY in the system.\
Can:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}create customers\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}create wallets\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}perform deposits and withdrawals (USDT)\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}convert assets between coins\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}create transaction requests\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}track down their transactions\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	c) 	CENTER_OPERATOR\
\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Responsible for approval of transaction requests. Can approve or reject requests. CANNOT create transactions directly. Ensures SEPARATION between creation and approval. \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	d)	 BRANCH_ADMIN \
\
Supervises a branch. Can view the wallets, employees, transaction requests, and transaction history of their branch. Focused on monitoring rather than execution.\
